Acceptance Criteria
- Loader handles API success and failure gracefully with fallback data.
- Summary metrics accurately reflect integration health across all records.
- Type filter correctly filters integrations by type (marketplace/courier/printer).
- Status badges display with correct colors and icons based on integration status.
- Credential status badges show rotation due/expired warnings appropriately.
- Webhook status badges indicate healthy/failing/paused states.
- Table rows expand to show credential and webhook details.
- Empty state handles gracefully when no integrations match filter.

